# Projects page - section title
msgid "Controlling a STK kart with hand gestures"
msgstr ""

# Projects page
msgid "A [fun project from 2024](https://www.reddit.com/r/SuperTuxKart/comments/1hdfz35/playing_supertuxkart_with_my_gaming_chair/) used hand gestures and chair orientation to control a kart. A script emulated a joystick using the data from a vision recognition system identifying gestures and from a phone on the player's chair which determined the turning angle depending on the chair's orientation."
msgstr ""

# Projects page
msgid "The driving level possible with this control method is surprisingly good considering how funny it looks!"
msgstr ""

